=== Etymology ===
[[tea]]+[[spoon]]

=== Noun ===
'''teaspoon''' ([[teaspoons]])

# a small spoon used to stir the contents of a [[cup]] or [[glass]]
# a unit of measure, worth one-third of a [[tablespoon]] or roughly five [[milliliter]]s.

